{"lemma":"سُرَّةُ","slug":"سُرَّةُ","root":"س.ر.ر","root_slug":"س-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19411","n19420"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"navel, belly button, umbilicus"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"centre"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root س ر ر (s r r), relating to the inside, innermost part; secret; pleasure; to please; to delight; etc."},"ipa":["/sur.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19411","headword_ar":"سَرَّهُ","root":"sr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the TA, has two contr. significations: for it is there stated that “ one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sararotuhu","text_ar":"سَرَرْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katamotuhu","text_ar":"كَتَمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sararotuhu","text_ar":"سَرَرْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolanotuhu","text_ar":"اَعْلَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ” and it is added that “ it will occur again soon: ” but it does not again occur in that work, nor have I found it in any other lexicon: I therefore think that it is a mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asorarotuhu","text_ar":"اَسْرَرْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first pers. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asar~ahu","text_ar":"اَسَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~ahu","text_ar":"سَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (MS,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masar~apN","text_ar":"مَسَرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which latter, from the explanations of it which will be found below, seems to be generally, if not only, as an inf. n., that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~a","text_ar":"سُرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~N","text_ar":"سُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is also syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the senses assigned to the latter below] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~aY","text_ar":"سُرَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasir~apN","text_ar":"تَسِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which last may be also an inf. n. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr~rhu","text_ar":"سرّرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. by Freytag as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~ahu","text_ar":"سَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense here following, but without an indication of any authority], (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, rejoiced him; gladdened him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him happy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaHahu","text_ar":"اَفْرَحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, K:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him to experience a pleasure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delight, and dilatation of the heart, of which there was no external sign:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~a","text_ar":"سُرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see above,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rejoiced; was joyful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glad;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was happy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, * K:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he experienced a pleasure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delight, and dilatation of the heart, of which there was no external sign;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~a bihi","text_ar":"سُرَّ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotasar~a","text_ar":"اِسْتَسَرَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rejoiced, was joyful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was happy, by reason of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~ahu","text_ar":"سَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor. as above, (TA,) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He saluted him with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the offering of what are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almasar~ap","text_ar":"المَسَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremities of sweet-smelling plants."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~ahu","text_ar":"سَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~N","text_ar":"سَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sir~N","text_ar":"سِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut his"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a child's)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sirar","text_ar":"سِرَر"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~","text_ar":"سُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"navel-string."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~a","text_ar":"سُرَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a child)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had his navel-string cut."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~ahu","text_ar":"سَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pierced him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrust him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[with a spear or the like,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~ap","text_ar":"سُرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"navel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waA_ino A^adobaruwA fahumu mano yusabo \n                      \n                     \n                        nasur~uhumu A_ino humu A^aqobaluwA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We pierce them in the navel if they advance; and if they retreat, they are those who are pierced in the podex;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yusabo","text_ar":"يُسَبْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yusab~u","text_ar":"يُسَبُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~a Alz~anoda","text_ar":"سَرَّ الزَّنْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~N","text_ar":"سَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put a piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the interior of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"znd","text_ar":"زند"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of stick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wood, for producing fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its extremity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inserting it in its interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that he might produce fire with it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~a zanodaka faA_in~ahu A^asar~u","text_ar":"سُرَّ زَنْدَكَ فَاـِنَّهُ اَسَرُّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fill up the interior of thy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"znd","text_ar":"زند"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that it may produce fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for it is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worn"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sar~a","text_ar":"سَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarirota","text_ar":"سَرِرْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yasar~u","text_ar":"يَسَرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, Sgh, L, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sararN","text_ar":"سَرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", remarked upon by MF as extr., [though it is agreeable with a general rule,] said of a man, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had a complaint of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~ap","text_ar":"سُرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"navel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, Sgh, L, K.) ―         -b2-  Also, aor. and inf. n. as in the next preceding case, said of a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had the pain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disorder, termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sararN","text_ar":"سَرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (IAar, M.)"}],"source_refs":["MS","S","O","K","Msb","TA","M","AHn","IAar","Sgh","L"]},{"entry_id":"n19420","headword_ar":"سُرَّةٌ","root":"sr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"navel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place from which the navel-string"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~","text_ar":"سُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has been cut off;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small cavity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow, of the belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the middle thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what remains of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sirar","text_ar":"سِرَر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~N","text_ar":"سُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"surarN","text_ar":"سُرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK erroneously"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sirarN","text_ar":"سِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~aAtN","text_ar":"سُرَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~apu Alfarasi","text_ar":"سُرَّةُ الفَرَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The navel of the horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the star, of Pegasus, that is in the head of Andromeda."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kzw.) ―         -b3-  [Hence likewise]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~apN","text_ar":"سُرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A perforation in the middle of a jar such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muzam~alap","text_ar":"مُزَمَّلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is fixed a tube of silver or lead, whence one drinks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 548.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where the water rests, in the furthest part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a watering-trough, or tank. (K, TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sir~N","text_ar":"سِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places, in the latter part of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":["M","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}